<div class="container-fluid movieTop pt-5 pb-3">
    <div class="row justify-content-center align-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-4 text-center text-white">
            <h3>The most beautiful colors of Africa</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 mb-4">We take our African origins to the top to reveal it to the world !</p>                        
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<%= render "layouts/flash" %>

<div class="container-fluid pt-5 pb-2" id='intro'>
    <div class="row justify-content-center align-content-center text-center">
        <div class="col-md-5">
            <h1>What about Origins</h1>
            <p class="mt-3 mb-4">Origins is an online distribution application for African films. Its main goal is to revive the African cinema in full fall, to put it forward already in the eyes of citizens but above all to reveal it beyond our borders. It will allow us Africans through the various works that will be broadcast to return to our sources that we have neglected so much for the benefit of Western realities. Origins will constitute the best digital panel through which African filmmakers will bring the realities of their countries to life for the entire world population.</p>                        
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid pt-3 pb-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center align-content-center text-center">
        <div class="col-md-5">
            <h1 id="title">Some Movies</h1>
            <p class="mt-3 mb-4">Now watch your best African films from home.</p>                        
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row justify-content-center align-content-center mt-4">
        <% if @movies.count > 0%>
            <% @movies.each do |movie| %>
                <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-md-5 mb-lg-0 d-flex align-items-stretch mb-4">
                    <div class="card shadow border-none" style="width: 100%;">
                        <% if movie.image && movie.image.url%>
                            <%= image_tag (movie.image_url), height: 230 %> 
                        <% else %>
                            <%= image_tag "no-images.jpg", height:230 %>
                        <% end %>
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title text-center font-weight-bold"><%= movie.name %></h5>
                            <p class="card-text"><%= movie.description %></p>
                            <p class="is_paying">
                                <% if movie.is_paying %>
                                    Paying: 600FCFA/Subscription: Standard
                                <% else %>
                                    Free-You can see this without pay
                                <%end%>
                            </p>
                            <p class="text-justify">Producted by : <%= movie.director %></p>
                            <p class="text-center mt-4"><%= link_to 'Watch yet' , movie_path(movie.id), class: "watch-button" %></p>                    
                        </div>
                    </div>        
                </div>
            <%end%>
        <% else %>
            <p> Nothing to show yet </p>
        <%end%>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid" >
    <div class="row justify-content-center align-content-center text-center pt-5 pb-3" id='subscribe'>
        <div class="col-md-5">
            <h3>Don't miss any of your best movies today</h3>
            <p class="mt-4 mb-4">Opt for a subscription offer and stay connected to Africa !</p> 
            <p class="text-center mt-4"><a href="#" class="subscribe-button">Get Subscriptions</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<%= render "layouts/footer" %>



